Doral.Coral Way Village, Florida:
Coral Way Village is a neighborhood of Westchester, a CDP and unincorporated community in Miami-Dade County, Florida, United States. Coral Way Village is located about 5 miles (8.0 km) west of Miami.


== Geography ==
It is located at 25.743°N 80.327°W﻿ / 25.743; -80.327, with an elevation 7 feet (2.1 m).
